{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2016/10/yarn.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b2ffda5d-d3e6-57ca-a6c4-5938567e7b23","html":"<p>Facebook has launched <a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Yarn</a>, an open source JavaScript package manager that promises faster and more reliable installs than the massively popular npm. The company says its new creation is capable of reducing install times from several minutes to just seconds in some cases – depending on the size of the packages you’re working with, of course.    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.duyet.net/2016/10/yarn.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ezPc9fi877Y/V_-5qaMEI4I/AAAAAAAAe6Y/qtoRjeGc45IgqUG93Ap-GRSyyf-hO7kkACK4B/s400/Yarn-796x398.jpg\"></a>\nThe easiest way to get started is to run:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g yarn\nyarn\n\nyarn add &lt;package&gt; # npm i --save &lt;package&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xn2w3G6Ilm0/V_-6KqLiOxI/AAAAAAAAe6g/UbU3OlotF0c54sw_KN6qch7lY6eR60bTACK4B/s1600/14658612_347000295637068_647258520764284928_n.gif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xn2w3G6Ilm0/V_-6KqLiOxI/AAAAAAAAe6g/UbU3OlotF0c54sw_KN6qch7lY6eR60bTACK4B/s1600/14658612_347000295637068_647258520764284928_n.gif\"></a>\nRead more:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://yarnpkg.com/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.facebook.com/posts/1840075619545360/yarn-a-new-package-manager-for-javascript\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://code.facebook.com/posts/1840075619545360/yarn-a-new-package-manager-for-javascript</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/2016/10/yarn.html","tagSlugs":["/tag/yarn/","/tag/js/","/tag/npm/","/tag/intro-js/","/tag/javascript/","/tag/node-js/","/tag/facebook/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-10-13T23:47:00.001+07:00","description":"Facebook has launched Yarn","tags":["Yarn","js","NPM","intro-js","javascript","Node.js","facebook"],"title":"Yarn: A new package manager for JavaScript","fbCommentUrl":"none"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2016/10/yarn.html"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","2672868365","401334301"]}